thread.title: BRIEF-X-Trade Brokers Dom Maklerski FY Net Profit Up At 93.0 Mln Zlotys

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-X-Trade Brokers Dom Maklerski FY Net Profit Up At 93.0 Mln Zlotys
text:
March 7 (Reuters) - X-TRADE BROKERS DOM MAKLERSKI SA :
* FY OPERATING REVENUE 273.8 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 250.6 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* FY NET PROFIT 93.0 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 77.7 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
* FY OPERATING PROFIT 128.3 MILLION ZLOTYS VERSUS 82.1 MILLION ZLOTYS YEAR AGO
